eina fangba paoda JunJun hairiba nupi da yam kana tanaraga fuba nupi ama yaori .Magi machanupi lwba nupa duga JunJun ga mari leinei hai adugimathak ta machanupi duga mayanupa duga khainei hai (not legally).Aduga matam khra leiraga amuk thungnahalli hai ahal aman ga wari sanaraga.Sigi manung sida nupi sigi mama na laman singningbagi party sida JunJun lakani khangbadagi mama sina mee mayam hwraga Dj twba mafam sida thomjankhibne hai JunJun hek ywrak a tabaga.Yam sengna hirabada lamansingning bagine moina attack twrido mee fahanaba natte.Mama sisu utlou ningol ni hai (lawai macha) utlou chaoba gi marimata ne hai.   Loose Translation in English:   According to an information i recieved theres a woman present who is after junJun and beating her up.The woman's son in law had/has an affair with JunJun and her daughter got separated from her son in law,not legally.After sometime they patched up with the invovlement of elders and [all.It](http://all.it/) is during this time that the mother in law of the man who had an affair with JunJun decided to exact revenge on JunJun.When she got hold of the news that a party is being organised and JunJun is going to be present the mother in law went with a group of people and attacked the party after they made sure that JunJun has arrived.I was even told that a drone was used just to confirmed that JunJun has arrived.What i want to make very clear to eveyone is the chain of event that took place was not to cleanse our society but it was a personal premedidated plan to exact revenge.The mother in law is a Utlou native and a relative of Utlou chaoba.         Conclusion : The meira paibi are being used to extract revenge on someone else for their own personal problem.Why is such an honourable organisation who stood up for justice had to get involved in these very personal matter?Is it for money?This organisation is not clean anymore.They have become one of the dirtiest organisation in manipur.Meira paibi should change their ways before the very people that are standing behind them turn against them.
